{"tid":345533,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"畀兄弟踢爆講蝗語，達哥仲死撐2","createTime":"2017-08-03T07:10:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T10:08:54.000Z","uid":25367,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"12919c157c202de9377c467757f466b859d553d5","tid":345533,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T07:10:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/7RgjHbOywJY?t=709\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7RgjHbOywJY%3Ft%3D709&d=oyvWpG%2BWImCkRdXppRAciwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=1a7cf0fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7RgjHbOywJY?t=709</a><br />\n<br />\n事源喺10:35，達哥講咗句「⋯技術革新，真係，未配套、未<span style=\"color: red;\">優化</span>好⋯」，跟住有兄弟喺chatroom提醒優化係蝗語，達哥仲死口唔認<br />\n「優化兩隻字係咪中文？」<br />\n「horizon入面台灣譯「劣化」，台灣翻譯係咪大陸話？」<br />\n<br />\n達哥解釋根本九唔搭八，首先香港、台灣、中國都係用緊「中文」，但部份用語上有分別，依家人哋話佢用中國用語佢反駁「優化兩隻字係咪中文？」根本廢話嚟<br />\n其次台灣文化上已經淪陷，咩個個都講小三、富二代，唔通台灣有用就唔叫大陸話？<br />\n<br />\n有興趣可以等達哥聽日upload chatroom版，睇睇當時有幾多兄弟屌緊達哥<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同場加映達語錄：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OfL4GABrWYQ?t=414\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOfL4GABrWYQ%3Ft%3D414&d=oyvWpG%2BWImCkRdXppRAciwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=e0dd6419\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OfL4GABrWYQ?t=414</a><br />\n2017-7-6： 一齊坑啲遊客錢<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XTRaCokDwoc?t=1520\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXTRaCokDwoc%3Ft%3D1520&d=oyvWpG%2BWImCkRdXppRAciwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=93034ae5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XTRaCokDwoc?t=1520</a><br />\n2017-7-11： 挖黑材料</blockquote>"},{"pid":"1456ae8d5beb969d258e9a40a57635004dfadafc","tid":345533,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T07:13:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d80cfa690c078c0f49b49aa4ed7e9cbfa8ffe89","tid":345533,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T08:32:40.000Z","msg":"香港人應該用改善，改良<br />\n中國人先用優化"},{"pid":"21ee413855fef62bb167eb0cb05f714e7e848adb","tid":345533,"uid":39921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T10:08:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你哋研究改善改良係由唔好變好就咁認真，查晒字典咁，依家就話明就ok<br />\n<br />\n簡體字仲簡單喇，你唔用？</blockquote><br />\n查字典同因應情況而用冇衝突<br />\n<br />\n同埋你唔好spin,我用唔用簡體字同優化係唔係蝗語係冇關"}]}